<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Ápice - Entrevista Online</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/entrevista-online.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/saladereuniao-inline.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
<%- include('../partials/menujovem') %>
</header>

<main class="interview-container">

<section class="interview-header">

<header>
<h1 class="interview-title">Entrevista Online</h1>
<p class="interview-subtitle">
Conecte-se com o entrevistador através de videochamada
</p>
</header>

</section>


<section class="video-section">

<article class="video-area">

<section class="video-placeholder">

<article class="participant-info">

<figure class="avatar">

<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
</svg>

</figure>

<p class="participant-name">
Aguardando entrevistador...
</p>

</article>


<nav class="video-controls">

<button class="control-btn camera-btn active" aria-label="Câmera">

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M17 10.5V7c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H4c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v10c0 .55.45 1 1 1h12c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-3.5l4 4v-11l-4 4z"/>
</svg>

</button>


<button class="control-btn mic-btn active" aria-label="Microfone">

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M12 14c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3V5c0-1.66-1.34-3-3-3S9 3.34 9 5v6c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3z"/>
<path d="M17 11c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5s-5-2.24-5-5H5c0 3.53 2.61 6.43 6 6.92V21h2v-3.08c3.39-.49 6-3.39 6-6.92h-2z"/>
</svg>

</button>


<button class="control-btn screen-btn" aria-label="Compartilhar tela">

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M20 18c1.1 0 1.99-.9 1.99-2L22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2H0v2h24v-2h-4zM4 6h16v10H4V6z"/>
</svg>

</button>


<button class="control-btn settings-btn" aria-label="Configurações">

<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M19.14,12.94c0.04-0.3,0.06-0.61,0.06-0.94c0-0.32-0.02-0.64-0.07-0.94l2.03-1.58c0.18-0.14,0.23-0.41,0.12-0.61 l-1.92-3.32c-0.12-0.22-0.37-0.29-0.59-0.22l-2.39,0.96c-0.5-0.38-1.03-0.7-1.62-0.94L14.4,2.81c-0.04-0.24-0.24-0.41-0.48-0.41 h-3.84c-0.24,0-0.43,0.17-0.47,0.41L9.25,5.35C8.66,5.59,8.12,5.92,7.63,6.29L5.24,5.33c-0.22-0.08-0.47,0-0.59,0.22L2.74,8.87 C2.62,9.08,2.66,9.34,2.86,9.48l2.03,1.58C4.84,11.36,4.8,11.69,4.8,12s0.02,0.64,0.07,0.94l-2.03,1.58 c-0.18,0.14-0.23,0.41-0.12,0.61l1.92,3.32c0.12,0.22,0.37,0.29,0.59,0.22l2.39-0.96c0.5,0.38,1.03,0.7,1.62,0.94l0.36,2.54 c0.05,0.24,0.24,0.41,0.48,0.41h3.84c0.24,0,0.43-0.17,0.47-0.41l0.36-2.54c0.59-0.24,1.13-0.56,1.62-0.94l2.39,0.96 c0.22,0.08,0.47,0,0.59-0.22l1.92-3.32c0.12-0.22,0.07-0.47-0.12-0.61L19.14,12.94z"/>
</svg>

</button>

</nav>

</section>

</article>

</section>


<section class="interview-info">

<article class="interview-details">

<h2>Informações da Entrevista</h2>

<ul class="details-list">

<li>
<span>Duração estimada: 30 minutos</span>
</li>

<li>
<span>Participantes: Você e o entrevistador</span>
</li>

<li>
<span>Sessão privada e segura</span>
</li>

</ul>

</article>


<article class="participants">

<h3>Participantes</h3>

<ul class="participants-list">

<li class="participant-item">

<figure class="participant-avatar">
<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4z"/>
</svg>
</figure>

<aside class="participant-details">
<p>Você</p>
<small class="ready">Pronto</small>
</aside>

</li>


<li class="participant-item">

<figure class="participant-avatar">
<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
<path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4z"/>
</svg>
</figure>

<aside class="participant-details">
<p>Entrevistador</p>
<small class="waiting">Aguardando</small>
</aside>

</li>

</ul>

</article>

</section>


<section class="interview-actions">

<button class="btn-join primary" id="joinInterview">
Entrar na Entrevista
</button>

<button class="btn-test secondary" id="testEquipment">
Testar Equipamentos
</button>

</section>


<section class="quick-settings">

<h3>Configurações Rápidas</h3>

<form>

<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked>
Câmera ligada por padrão
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox" checked>
Microfone ligado por padrão
</label>

<label>
<input type="checkbox">
Gravar entrevista
</label>

</form>

</section>

</main>

<script src="/js/entrevista-online.js"></script>
<script src="/js/script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>